'''Ama Ata Aidoo''', ''née'' '''Christina Ama Aidoo''' (wavutse ku ya 23 Werurwe 1942) ni umwanditsi wo muri [[Gana]], umusizi, umwanditsi w'amakinamico n'umunyeshuri<ref>Ama Ata Aidoo | Ghanaian writer | Britannica <nowiki>https://www.britannica.com</nowiki> › ... › Novelists A-K</ref>.  Yari Minisitiri w’uburezi uyobowe na Jerry Rawlings administration <ref>A Profile of Ama Ata Aidoo - Literary Mama <nowiki>https://literarymama.com</nowiki> › departments › 2016/02 › a-...</ref>. Mu 2000, yashinze Fondasiyo ya Mbaasem yo guteza imbere no gushyigikira umurimo w’abanditsi b’abagore [[Afurika|b’abanyafurika.]]<ref>Books by Ama Ata Aidoo - ThriftBooks <nowiki>https://www.thriftbooks.com</nowiki> › ama-ata-aidoo</ref>  

== Ubuzima bwo hambere ==
Aidoo yavutse ku ya 23 Werurwe 1942 i Saltpond mu mu gace ko hagati muri [[Gana]], Amakuru amwe arimo Megan Behrent, kaminuza ya Brown, na [[Afurika]] Ninde wavuze ko yavutse ku ya 31 Werurwe 1940<ref>(Christina) Ama Ata Aidoo Biography <nowiki>https://biography.jrank.org</nowiki> › pages › Aidoo-Christina-...</ref>. Yakuriye mu rugo rw'umwami wa Fante, umukobwa wa Nana Yaw Fama, umutware wa Abeadzi Kyiakor, na Maame Abasema. <ref>[https://www.taylorfrancis.com/books/e/9780203058558/chapters/10.4324/9780203058558-4 "AMA ATA AIDOO (1942-)"], ''Postcolonial African Writers'', Routledge, 1998.</ref> Yakuze mugihe cy' [[ubwongereza]] bushya bwa neocolonialism bwaberaga mu gihugu cye<ref>Biography of Ama Ata Aidoo - Poem Hunter <nowiki>https://www.poemhunter.com</nowiki> › Ama Ata Aidoo</ref>. Sekuru yiciwe na neocolonialiste, ibyo bikaba byaratumye se yibanda ku kamaro ko kwigisha abana n'imiryango yo mu mudugudu n'amateka yabayeho<ref>The Art of Ama Ata Aido | A documentary film by Yaba Badoe (amaatafilm.com)</ref>. Ibi byatumye afungura ishuri rya mbere mu mudugudu wabo maze bituma Aidoo yiga mu ishuri ryisumbuye rya Wesley Girls aho yahisemo bwa mbere ko ashaka kuba umwanditsi<ref>Celebrating Writers Who Defy All the Odds - The New York ... <nowiki>https://www.nytimes.com</nowiki> › 1997/10/22 › books › celebrat...</ref>.  

== Uburezi ==
Aidoo yize amashuri yisumbuye ya Wesley Girls i Cape Coast,  kuva 1961 kugeza 1964<ref>Nobody could tell me writing was a man's job - DVV International <nowiki>https://www.dvv-international.de</nowiki> › editions › interviews</ref>. Amashuri yisumbuye, yiyandikishije muri kaminuza ya Gana, muri Legon aho yakuye impamyabumenyi ya Bachelor of Arts mu Cyongereza ndetse yandika n'ikinamico ye ya mbere yise ''“Dilemma of Ghost”'', mu 1964. <ref>[http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/10410/Ama-Ata-Aidoo "Ama Ata Aidoo"], ''Encyclopædia Britannica''.</ref> Ikinamico yasohowe na Longman umwaka wakurikiyeho, bituma Aidoo aba umukinnyi wa mbere  w’amakinamico wo muri [[Afurika]]. <ref>Naana Banyiwa Horne, "Aidoo, Ama Ata", ''Who's Who in Contemporary Women's Writing'', 2001, Routledge.</ref>

== Filime ==
Niwe filime ya documentaire ya 2014, ''Ubuhanzi bwa Ama Ata Aidoo'', yakozwe na Yaba Badoe . <ref name="AAAA">[http://amaatafilm.com/ "The Art of Ama Ata Aidoo - a film by Yaba Badoe"], official website.</ref> <ref>Beti Ellerson, [http://africanwomenincinema.blogspot.co.uk/2013/12/yaba-badoe-talks-about-documentary-film.html "Yaba Badoe talks about the documentary film project 'The Art of Ama Ata Aidoo'"], African Women in Cinema, December 2013.</ref> <ref>Shakira Chambas and Sionne Neely, [http://www.awdf.org/the-art-of-ama-ata-aidoo-documentary-film-launch/ "The Art of AMA ATA AIDOO: Documentary Film Launch"], African Women’s Development Fund, 26 September 2014.</ref>

== Inyandiko ==
Ikinamico ya Aidoo irimo ''The Dilemma of Ghost'', yakorewe i Legon mu 1964 (yatangajwe bwa mbere 1965) na Pittsburgh mu 1988, na ''Anowa'', yasohowe mu 1971 ikorerwa i Londres mu 1991<ref>Her Story | BBC World Service</ref>. 
